_sText:
A port of de_piranesi_cz to CS:S, found in 2003 hl1ports leak. Most likely, this is the first ever map made for Counter-Strike: Source.

The map is dated September 24, 2003 (the date is most likely overwritten and the map could have been made earlier) and although this is a port, there are differences from the Condition Zero version, such as: the presence of models, displacements and water from Source engine. Also this map contains some unused assets that are in the game files. 

In the leak, the original name of the map was "devtest", but I renamed it for better recognition. I also added HDR support and cubemaps.
